N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 50.3 - Method of disinfecting

State Regulations

Except as herein provided, the disinfecting of the
above-mentioned premises shall be done by approved disinfectors using equipment
and materials at recommended dilutions approved by the
commissioner. Notes
